cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IT, cs.ST, cs.SY 

This paper deals with statistical estimation and generalization error in learning machines, which are core topics in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG and cs.AI are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses information criteria and their application, which are related to information theory (cs.IT) and statistical inference (cs.ST). Finally, the paper deals with hidden variables and hierarchical structures, which are common in control systems (cs.SY).
